		{
			"id": "http://curt.micro.blog/2017/07/03/it-is-more.html",
			"content_html": "<p>“It is more violent … has worse health outcomes … America’s average levels of academic achievement lag … Fewer Americans vote” —<a href=\"https://www.theatlantic.com/politics/archive/2017/07/the-sunset-of-american-exceptionalism/532548/\">David Frum</a></p>\n",
